text: Seaside Heights is a borough in Ocean County, New Jersey. According to the 2020 Census, the borough population was 2,440. Summer population explodes upwards to thirty thousand persons because the city is a resort community with beaches, bars, and clubs. The Seaside Heights Boardwalk received exposure through shows on MTV, such as Jersey Shore. == References == Category:Boroughs in New Jersey Category:Ocean County, New Jersey
title: Seaside Heights, New Jersey
